 int burnham house family room moments later 
 angela lays back on the couch as lester moves in over her unbuttoning her blouse she seems disconnected from happening not fighting it but not really taking part in it either lester pulls her blouse open exposing her breasts he kisses her neck and starts working his way down 
 int burnham house jane s room continuous 
 ricky and jane fully clothed lie curled up on bed 
 janeare you scared 
 rickyi get scared 
 janemy parents will try to find me 
 rickymine and i always figured have to wait until i was could go further than new york chicago europe even 
