 angela still want to do it i just thought i should tell you you know in case you wondered why i better 
 honey 
 he smiles and brushes a lock of hair from her forehead aftera moment she smiles back shyly he lingers above her drinking in this vision of her oh man and then he sighs and moves off of her she looks bewildered 
 wrong 
 lester gathers her clothes form the floor and hands them toher angela is stunned 
 angela thought you said i was beautiful 
 lesteryou are beautiful 
 lester grabs a blanket from the back of the couch and drapesit around her shoulders covering her nakedness 
 lester so beautiful and i would be a very lucky man but 
 he smiles and shakes his head humiliated she starts to cry 
 angelai feel so stupid 
 
 he hugs her letting her put her head on his shoulder stroking her hair and rocking her gently 
 sorry 
 lester takes her by the shoulders and looks at her serious 
 lesteryou have nothing to be sorry about 
 but she keeps crying lester hugs her again we hear a loudclap of thunder outside 
 lester okay okay 
 ext robin hood trail the same time 
 the ml pulls onto robin hood trail 
 int ml continuous 
 close on eyes reflected in the mirror 
 carolyni refuse to be a victim 
 in the mirror we see her turn her head 
 her pov driving in slow motion past the burnham house the red door illuminated by the porch light stands out even in the pouring rain 
 ext robin hood trail continuous 
 close on angela eating a turkey sandwich 
 i was starving 
 seated at the snack bar in the kitchen once again fully dressed from the tv in the next room we can hear a canned laughter 
 lester in his sweatpants and a puts a jar ofmayonnaise back in the refrigerator then crosses to the sink to rinse off a knife 
 lesterwant me to make you another one 
 angelano no no fine 
 he turns to her and cocks an eyebrow 
 
 angelayes stop asking me that 
 lesterokay just checking 
 he turns off the faucet and joins her at the snack reaches for the beer and takes a swig then passes it to lester he takes it but drink 
 angelai mean yeah still a little weirded feel better thanks 
 a long beat as lester studies her then 
 jane 
 angelawhat do you mean 
 lesteri mean her life is she happy is she miserable like to know and die before ever tell me about it 
 angela shifts uncomfortably does she tell him about janeand ricky finally 
 really happy she thinks in love 
 angela rolls her eyes at how silly this is lester justsmiles 
 for her 
 an awkward beat 
 angelahow are you 
 lester seems somewhat taken aback by this question 
 been a long time since anybody asked me that about it great 
 they just sit there smiling at each other then 
 have to go to the bathroom 
 she jumps up and crosses off lester watches her go thenrubs his face suddenly tired 
 great 
 something at the edge of the snack bar suddenly catches hiseye and he reaches for 
 close on a framed photograph as he picks it up the same one we saw earlier of him carolyn and a jane taken several years ago at an amusement park startling how happy they look 
 close on lester as he studies the picture spellbound just as the colonel was when looking at the photo of himself and the other young serviceman we suddenly become aware of the sound of water dripping pulled out of his reverie lester glances up at 
 water dripping slowly from the kitchen faucet 
 angle on lester in profile he puts the photograph down props his elbows on the snack bar clasps his hands together and rests his chin on them thinking this almost gives him the appearance of praying and he suddenly appears older more mature and then he smiles the deep satisfied smile of a man who just now understands the punch line of a joke he heard long ago 
 after a beat the barrel of a gun rises up behind his head 
 angle on an arrangement of roses in a vase on theopposite counter deep crimson against the white tile wall from the tv in the next room we still hear canned laughter then a gunshot suddenly rings out echoing unnaturally instantly the tile is sprayed with blood the same deep crimson as the roses the canned laughter continues and then the sound fades as everything starts to brighten and the screen goes white 
 we hear a rush of wind 
 fade in 
 ext sky day 
 flying above a snowy white blanket of clouds lester comes into view below us flying wearing the same pajamas and plaid flannel robe he wore in his dream at the beginning 
 lester say your entire life flashes in front of your eyes when you die 
 int burnham house bedroom night 
 looking down at ricky and jane curled up on bed the night of murder we hear a gunshot from downstairs ricky and jane look at each other alarmed 
 lester 
 not really your entire life 
 int burnham house powder room night 
 angela stands in front of the mirror brushing her hair wehear the gunshot again angela freezes frightened 
 just the moments that stood out 
 
 
